text: I was told by everyone, to go to One Roof, they could help me to get emergency section 8 voucher. I am living in my car. The lady Jennifer Harrell, was the person to call. All I am getting is the run around. She said in order for her to help, I would have to be in a shelter, homeless, or living in my car. Well, I have been in my car for over a week now... Here is the problem, they do not care about homeless, they are not government funded, if they were, we would not have so many homeless...
